obin-inducing agents.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/57365/', '', 'Lidocaine, Procaine, Tetracaine, Lidocaine, Clemastine, Tetracaine, Mepyramine, Diphenhydramine, Tripelennamine, Doxepin, Pheniramine, More', 'Prilocaine, Meloxicam', 1767369485);
